query:
SELECT u.email, s.platform, s.status, s.trial_start, s.trial_end, s.selected_plan, s.created_at
FROM subscriptions s
JOIN users u ON s.user_id = u.id
WHERE u.email = 'comeeconomics@gmail.com' AND s.platform = 'rxguard'
ORDER BY s.created_at DESC
LIMIT 5;
